title: and Valuation (Amendment) Act 2022 (Commencement of Certain Provisions)
heading: 2. The 4th day of November 2022 is appointed as the day on which
text_raw:
2. The 4th day of November 2022 is appointed as the day on which 
sections 2, 8 and 9 of the Planning and Development, Maritime and Valuation 
(Amendment) Act 2022 (No. 29 of 2022) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

2 November, 2022. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 4th November, 2022.
